cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modelling and text classification tasks. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new model based on self-attention mechanism for better performance in language modelling. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves training neural networks for language tasks. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it proposes a new model for machine translation.
